OL,3,CRail company stocks low alcohol beer
OL,4,Cto curb drunken disorder over Christmas
OL,6,FA rail company has introduced a low
OL,7,Falcohol beer to their onboard shop in
OL,8,Fan effort to reduce drunken disorder
OL,9,Fover the Christmas period and make
OL,10,F"rail safety tasty".
OL,12,FYear on year, Avanti West Coast has
OL,13,Fseen the amount of alcohol related
OL,14,Fincidents soar between the end of
OL,15,FNovember and New Years Eve.
OL,17,FIn the 2023 festive period, 115
OL,18,Fincidents were reported by staff in
OL,19,Fwhich disruptive passengers were
OL,20,Fvisibly drunk.
