OL,3,CRail company stocks low alcohol beer
OL,4,Cto curb drunken disorder over Christmas
OL,6,FTo reduce these numbers, passengers
OL,7,Fwill now be offered a can of 'Safety
OL,8,FThirst'; a low alcohol alternative
OL,9,Fbeer.
OL,11,FThe 0.5 percent pale ale will be
OL,12,Fstocked onboard the operator's trains,
OL,13,Fwhich run from London to Manchester,
OL,14,FLiverpool, and Edinburgh to encourage
OL,15,Fthose enjoying festivities to drink
OL,16,Fresponsibly while travelling on the
OL,17,Frail network.
