OL,3,CRail company stocks low alcohol beer
OL,4,Cto curb drunken disorder over Christmas
OL,6,FThe initiative is being backed by UK's
OL,7,Fleading alcohol charity Drinkaware and
OL,8,Fthe Rail Safety and Standards Board
OL,9,F(RSSB).
OL,11,FMark Phillips, CEO at the Rail Safety
OL,12,Fand Standards Board (RSSB) said: "This
OL,13,Fis a fantastic initiative by Avanti
OL,14,FWest Coast. Every year in the run up
OL,15,Fto Christmas, our data shows an
OL,16,Fincrease in passengers being injured
OL,17,Fafter enjoying a little too much
OL,18,Fseasonal hospitality.
OL,26,@tD@bOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
