OL,3,CRail company stocks low alcohol beer
OL,4,Cto curb drunken disorder over Christmas
OL,6,F"Everyone should enjoy themselves, but
OL,7,Fby drinking responsibly they will stay
OL,8,Fsafe and help reduce pressure on the
OL,9,Frailway at one of its busiest times."
OL,11,FFigures compiled by the RSSB show the
OL,12,Fnumber of accidents on the GB mainline
OL,13,Fnetwork last year where intoxication
OL,14,Fwas a possible factor increased by 45%
OL,15,Fduring the Christmas period.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@eO]
