OL,3,CRail company stocks low alcohol beer
OL,4,Cto curb drunken disorder over Christmas
OL,6,FTo promote the campaign, a choir made
OL,7,Fup of Avanti West Coast colleagues
OL,8,Fperformed a reworked version of the
OL,9,Fsong "Jingle Bells" replacing it with
OL,10,FSafety Thirst focusing on safety
OL,11,Fmessages.
OL,13,FDave Whitehouse, Director of Safety,
OL,14,FSecurity and Environment at Avanti
OL,15,FWest Coast, said:"We want the railway
OL,16,Fto be the transport of choice when
OL,17,Fpeople are heading out to enjoy
OL,18,Fthemselves during the festive season
OL,19,Fand while our customers are out on the
OL,20,Fnetwork, we want them to be safe too.
OL,26,@qD@FOUqD@SO]wD@SOU
