OL,4,Cto curb drunken disorder over Christmas
OL,6,FKaren Tyrell, CEO of Drinkaware, said:
OL,7,F"This is a great move. Our research
OL,8,Fshows that low and no-alcohol drinks
OL,9,Fare increasing in popularity, with
OL,10,Faround a third of people now using
OL,11,Fthem to moderate their drinking.
OL,13,F"Creating a low alcohol option for
OL,14,Fthose travelling on Avanti West Coast
OL,15,Fwill help people cut back on their
OL,16,Fdrinking.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
